# Post-change workflow (this project)

## Prettier

Deploy runs `prettier --check` (see `.github/workflows/deploy.yml`). After editing files that Prettier formats (JS, HTML, CSS, JSON, MD, YAML, etc.), run:

`npx --yes prettier@3.5.3 --write .`

—or `--write` only on paths touched. If you bump the Prettier version in CI, update this command to match.

Respect `.prettierignore` (e.g. generated `style.css`, `sw.js`, `dist/`).

## README

Update [README.md](README.md) when the change affects how someone clones, runs, builds, deploys, or uses tooling—not for every trivial code edit.
